short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: UEU-MEET Video Conference that allows you to schedule E-Meetings

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple extension that allows you to schedule Universitas Esa Unggul Meetings and stream your desktop into UEU-MEET conferences.

UEU-MEET is an OpenSource (Apache) WebRTC JavaScript application that uses Jitsi Videobridge to provide high quality, scalable video conferences. 

This extension provides the Universitas Esa Unggul site with desktop streaming functionality over Chrome.
